= TTF_SetFontHinting =

Set FreeType hinter settings.

== Syntax ==

<syntaxhighlight lang='c'>
void TTF_SetFontHinting(TTF_Font *font, int hinting);
</syntaxhighlight>

== Function Parameters ==

{|
|'''font'''
|[[TTF_Font]] handle
|-
|'''hinting'''
|hinting flag
|}

== Remarks ==

Setting it clears already generated glyphs, if any, from the cache.

